@page "/docs/dark-mode"

<PageTitle>Dark Mode - Tldraw.Blazor Docs</PageTitle>

<div class="docs-content">
    <h1>Dark Mode</h1>
    <p class="docs-lead">Toggle between light and dark themes.</p>

    <h2 id="toggle">
        Toggle
        <a class="docs-anchor" href="#toggle">#</a>
    </h2>
    <p>Click the 🌙 button in the toolbar to toggle dark mode. The setting persists across sessions.</p>

    <h2 id="scope">
        Affected Components
        <a class="docs-anchor" href="#scope">#</a>
    </h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Toolbar background and text</li>
        <li>Style Panel</li>
        <li>Context Menu</li>
        <li>Minimap</li>
        <li>Pages Panel</li>
        <li>Keyboard Shortcuts help</li>
    </ul>
    <p>The canvas itself uses a fixed light background (#F5F5F5) for clarity.</p>
</div>
